<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Nex - Powerful and flexible Nostr relay written in Elixir</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";
      color: #e2e8f0;
      background-color: #0f172a;
    }
    .panel {
      max-width: 16rem;
      padding: 1rem 2rem 2rem;
      background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
    }
    .title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #0f172a;
      text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.8);
    }
    .version {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #a855f7;
      text-shadow: 0 0 2px rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.8);
    }
    .strapline {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }
    .link {
      margin: 1rem 0 0;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .link a {
      color: #60a5fa;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 300ms ease-out;
    }
    .link a:hover {
      color: #f0abfc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="panel">
    <h1 class="title">
      nex
      <span class="version">v<%= version %></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="strapline">Powerful and flexible Nostr relay written in Elixir.</p>
    <p class="link">
      <a href="https://github.com/lebrunel/nex" target="_blank">github.com/lebrunel/nex</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
